Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:45.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,Catch us if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's gotten so bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Mom, I've gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm fine even if I'm on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm ready to help Natsume now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.17,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}The Fox Child{\c&H64A2D6&\4c&H6A99BE&}'s{\c\4c} Watch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.17,title,,0,0,0,,The Fox Child{\c&H015C07&}'s{\c} Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh, I'm going on a trip with Shigeru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,You remember Yasui-san, from the Kariba Hot Springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,You know, the place you got this teacup for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, near the summer resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,In truth, I've been in contact with him since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,He is having a pottery class, and wanted me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Touko-san's coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting some friends at the supermarket on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,You two just go and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:11.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,Though it's said to be a class, it's really a chance for the kids from the neighborhood to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you're not up for it, I can turn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Do you have plans with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, I'd love to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go together. {It's settled then.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Were you groaning just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must have slept out of your mind, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,A tiny wound like that? It'd be fine after I lick it a couple more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was planning on having the middle-rank youkai take care of you while I'm at the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,A hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume, you're going to a hot spring without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,See, you shouldn't be moving around yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,The Kariba springs aren't going to cure a youkai's wounds, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hinoe! Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard you were injured, so I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that how you greet your visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,You were hit by a cursed arrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's going to take long to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei said it'd heal in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,That wasn't far from the truth either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,To us youkai, it's just a blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:51.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even so, it's difficult even for a powerful youkai like Madara to regain all his energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,I guess a trip is out of the question then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to apologize to Shigeru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the herb, "oborosou" grows there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oborosou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's a youkai herb that normal people can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:17.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,It grows on trees that are centuries old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Grind it up and apply to the wound. It does wonders on youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,Nah, I don't need that. Take me to the hot springs, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,To say the truth, I wanted to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,Madara-sama, we've come to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Visit... Visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard that the white pig was injured, so I've come to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Hinoe-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,How about a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,I love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come on, not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,You guys are too noisy–
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,It would probably worsen his injuries if I left him here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,You didn't sleep well, Takashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was up packing all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,There's a restaurant on the way there that sells delicious takeouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,We will have that for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is this what it feels like be on a trip with your own dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's a bit embarrassing, but I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:39.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,But sitting across from him, I don't really know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Young people aren't interested in pottery, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,I feel bad making you come here for my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,I like the teacup we got last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,For a long time, I've liked the touch of pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:59.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,It looks cold, but feels warm{figuratively, I guess}... like the clay is still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,So, I've always thought of baking one myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,Having a conversation like this with Shigeru-san is something new to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is something humans wear on their wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:03.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,You come here often to look at those trains used by the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm none other than the rock you're stepping on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say I'm the living form of the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,People used to call me the Stone God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Stone God... You are a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,The humans decided on their own to worship me, that's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.06,natsume,,0,0,0,,You come here to watch the trains often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are they that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:35.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, I thought that Natsume might return, so I come here to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:40.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,Although I'm disappointed everytime, I'm certain Natsume will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume... A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Natsume's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're wearing a watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,A watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's a device humans used to track time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,It wasn't moving a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:04.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing that? Do you wish to become human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Become human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, I want to be a great fox, just like my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then, it's useless to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,Because it measures human time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,Human time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume came to see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm not as weak as before, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's so windy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's been a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder how he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,He lives with Natsume.
