Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.29,woodsign,,0,0,0,,{\move(1278,1012.5,1278,217.5)\be1}Yasuian{\fscx60\fscy60}\NPottery\NSchool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara-san, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,You came to get the teacups last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's carrying a human item!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,The beast thinks he's human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,How dare him, he can't even do a proper transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:42.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,This won't be as easy as the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! You can have it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's why I said he's a beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:13.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,Mom said never to go near that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:17.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is where we'll be firing the pieces we make in pottery class tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,And it'd be ready the following day, for you all to take home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must all be tired by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,There's a hot spring out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,If this goes on, I won't be able to get close to Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's change over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,Compared to when you just moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,Everybody still says I'm frail, and makes fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're much stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can tell, since we live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,What a nice hot spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,What is Natsume doing at such a dangerous place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:42.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Didn't he come here to see me?
