Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's only alive when I'm moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,Be sure not to trap any air in the clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Skinny brother, lift me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why won't I get any bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,We're going to start burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun, can you help me with the kiln?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:02.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,Beast child, stop seeing the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you don't, one party will always be left with the sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:16.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,Every entity in this world has his own time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,And they're not always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,Humans have humans', youkai have youkai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,And beasts, their own definition of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:32.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume and you don't share the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:45.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must find a partner, have children, and teach them wisely, just like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,That is how a beast should live his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,In the same way, Natsume has his own time to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:59.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,And that is very different than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:03.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,Does the Stone God lives in his own time too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,I live the time of a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:11.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was here long before there was humans or youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:17.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,And I'll stay here until time abruptly ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here always?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:24.06,natsume,,0,0,0,,The day I leave this place, is the day I disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's the meaning of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,To me, it wasn't really that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't short either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,We close this up like this while it burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:47.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,And the clay will harden into the form we gave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,After that, we can start with the coloring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Now, we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi, is there anything you'd like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yasui-san said he's going to show me some of his pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:04.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll take this chance to explore around for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought I would see him in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Guess I was too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,He has his own life, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,I remember you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Master Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that little fox is up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's no good, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's grown into a little delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,A delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,We don't know what to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just look at this scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,You two weren't bullying him again, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,There's one other thing I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Mom, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be with Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't get so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Master Natsume is here, we wouldn't misbehave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,You met him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,He wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,But he is pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,He is looking for some kind of herb that is growing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:24.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,Herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:29.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's called "oborosou". Seems like it grows on the ancient trees here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oborosou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's about time to apply the colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,If only I could do something for Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,We'll bake them for another twelve hours, and they'll be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can't be up there, Sensei. You should be resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,A thunderstorm is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, he'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll give that to Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume! Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,You got those for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume, the Stone God saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:33.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day I leave this place, is the day I disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the meaning of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,The Stone God told me not to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Said that one of us would have sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,But... but that's not true, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,The watch is broken now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,...but it was working before, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:21:01.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,I remembered it all... meeting the Stone God, what we talked about, and how he saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:06.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure Natsume and I will... will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:16.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't know the whole story why he would want the fox child to forget about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:22.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,But I think I can understand what the Stone God is trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:27.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Humans and youkai have very different lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:32.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,He must have seen it more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nyangoro's on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Very well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great? Nyangoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:19.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Although we only meet for a brief moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter, I will still cherish every moment.
