Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,I got acquainted with a youkai again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:05.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,The cultural festival must have a bunny girl cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,We can't have bunny girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:08.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,The festival is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:12.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to it too, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:15.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,Set up a kitty cafe where I'll be the center of attention!
